BANGAPHEZU kuka-1 000 abantu asebehaqwe yigciwane leCovid-19 eGauteng  njengoba lesi sifundazwe sesinabantu abangu12 193. Abantu njengamanje asebehaqwe yileli gciwane bangaphezu kuka8 664 kusukela ngoLwesibili, okusho ukuthi sebengaphezu ngo1 300 uma kuqhathaniswa nesibalo sangoMsombuluko. UMnyango wezeMpilo kulesi sifundazwe umemezele lezi zibalo namhlanje.  Kunezidumbu ezingaphezu kweziyisithupha eziphumile, ezinhlanu zazo okungezabantu baseGoli. IGoli linabantu abahlanu abahaqeka ngosuku. isibalo sabantu asebesindile kulesi sifo sesifiyelele ku3 442 futhi zingu572 iziguli ezilashwa ezibhedlela zomphakathi nezizimele.   Isifundazwe sithe bangaphezu kuka13 000 kubantu abahaqene  ABAHAQEKILE ASEBESHONILE ASEBESINDILE ABASAGULA Gauteng 12193 87 3442 8664 Johannesburg 6071 47 1875 4149 Ekurhuleni 2443 20 809 1614 Tshwane 1710 10 405 1295 West Rand 912 8 288 616 Sedibeng 339 2 65 272 ECity of Johannesburg sebengu6071 asebehaqekile ESoweto nase-Inner City kuyaqhubeka nokuba yizidleke zabahaqekile esifundeni saseGoli, njengoba sanda nje isibalo. ISandton neRandburg inabantu abangu500 abasahaqekile.  IGauteng ayidalulanga izibalo zasebeshonile kwisifunda ngasinye. Isifunda  A: Diepsloot, Kya Sands, Dainfern, Midrand, Lanseria, Fourways, Ivory Park – bangu571 abahaqekile, bangu318 abasaphila negciwane isifunda B: Randburg, Rosebank, Emmarentia, Greenside, Melville, Mayfair, Northcliff, Parktown, Parktown North – bangu779 , 543 abasahaqekile Isifunda C: Roodepoort, Constantia Kloof, Northgate, Florida, Bram Fishersville – bangu659 abahaqekile, bangu480 abasaphila negciwane. Isifunda D: Doornkop, Soweto, Dobsonville, Protea Glen – bangu1017 abahaqekile nabangu720 abasaphila negciwane. Isifunda E: Alexandra, Wynberg, Sandton, Orange Grove, Houghton –bangu 919 abahaqekile nabangu559 abasaphila negciwane Isifunda F: Inner City, Johannesburg South – bangu1 411 abahaqekile nabangu1093 abasaphila negciwane Isifunda G:  Orange Farm, Weilers Farm, Ennerdale, Lenasia, Eldorado Park, 